&lt;li&gt;Ability to communicate across internal and external vendors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research filing components on various government databases and public record sources, including state-specific compliance requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prioritize and manage a high-volume and time-sensitive workflow from submission to completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate with vendors such as Registered Agents Inc. if additional information is needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate across internal teams for additional information or support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calling both clients and serving parties to notify them that an SOP has been served.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams as needed to ensure accurate SOP processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist customers with questions regarding product, service, process, billing, and general client concerns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Making phone calls to clients on a daily basis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
