&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience reviewing and processing legal documents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of current Secretary/Department of State corporate statutes and filing requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Salesforce or other equivalent CRM applications.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to identify urgent fulfillment while staying on top of high-volume customer requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with the fast-paced and ever-changing environment of a growing tech startup.&lt;/li&gt;
